@* Evaluation *@
<div id="evaluationModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
        <div class="modal-content">

            <div class="modal-header">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
                <h4 class="modal-title" align="center">Online Evaluation</h4>
            </div>

            <div class="modal-body">
                <p>
                    The online CareerPathfinder test has been developed by an expert doctor in the field.
                </p>
                <p>
                    The test focuses on key factors such as personality traits and abilities to accurately
                    predict the career that best suits you. You will engage in this comprehensive test through
                    a series of various questions that will link you to suitable careers.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Understand yourself better with this specialised self-discovery test.
                </p>
                <div>
                    <div class="modal-footer">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@* Analysis *@
<div id="analysisModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
        <div class="modal-content">

            <div class="modal-header">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
                <h4 class="modal-title" align="center">Analysis</h4>
            </div>

            <div class="modal-body">
                Once the CareerPathfinder test has been successfully attempted and submitted, it will then be 
                received by the doctor himself. The doctor will then analyse the data and determine the likely 
                careers for you.
                <div>

                    <div class="modal-footer">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@* Results *@
<div id="resultsModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
        <div class="modal-content">

            <div class="modal-header">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
                <h4 class="modal-title" align="center">Results Feedback</h4>
            </div>

            <div class="modal-body">
                The finalisation of your results will be communicated to you together with a report on your possible 
                career options giving you the peace of mind of successfully chosing a future career that matches your 
                unique assesment profile.
                <div>

                    <div class="modal-footer">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Call to Action Bar -->
<div class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="calltoaction-wrapper">
                    <h3>Unlock your future. Take the test today</h3> <br>
                    <h4>
                        The test will take you just 90 minutes to complete, with the
                        option to save your progress and continue later. Are you ready
                        to unlock your future?
                    </h4><br>
                    <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Test", new {area="member"})" class="btn btn-red">Yes! Let's Begin!</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<!-- End Call to Action Bar -->
